author: CatherineW
title: CatherineW
text:
Since I discovered Elevate Styles about a year ago, every purchase I have made have been sent/delivered in a timely fashion, and 85% was sent faster than I expected it to be delivered, bottom-line, delivery has been 100% satisfactory.
The products I have purchased are what I requested and I am completely satisfied. I can only hope Elevate Styles continue to carry my products thanks you so much Elevate Styles! Sincerely C Webster
